    "code": "import flopscope as fnp\n\na = fnp.array([[1, 2], [3, 4]])\n\na\n\nfnp.transpose(a)\n\na = fnp.array([1, 2, 3, 4])\n\na\n\nfnp.transpose(a)\n\na = fnp.ones((1, 2, 3))\n\nfnp.transpose(a, (1, 0, 2)).shape\n\na = fnp.ones((2, 3, 4, 5))\n\nfnp.transpose(a).shape\n\na = fnp.arange(3*4*5).reshape((3, 4, 5))\n\nfnp.transpose(a, (-1, 0, -2)).shape",
